description: The trail continues on its way following the slope of the mountain as it rises to the south.  The stars shine through the thin mountain air in a dazzling display of celestial light.

The trail continues on its way following the slope of the mountain as it rises to the south.  Some hearty butterflyweed attracts a variety of insects, which float in a chaotic dance above a rising thermal.
title: [Whistler's Pass, Alpine Tundra]
